abstract: We have seen great progress in authentication over the last few years, but authorization is still challenging for most engineering teams.  Enter Fine Grained Authorization, an approach that simplifies access management by leveraging Relationship-Based Access Control (ReBAC), enhancing security, and reducing administrative overhead.
